&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.2.4.4、建立测试类</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;测试类&nbsp;在src/test/java中建立&nbsp;，下面测试类中&nbsp;注释掉的部分是不使用&nbsp;Spring时，一般情况下的一种测试方法&nbsp;；如果使用了&nbsp;Spring&nbsp;那么就可以使用注解的方式来引入配置文件和类，然后再将&nbsp;service&nbsp;接口对象注入，就可以进行测试了。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;如果测试成功，表示&nbsp;Spring&nbsp;和&nbsp;Mybatis&nbsp;已经整合成功了&nbsp;。输出信息使用的是&nbsp;Log4j&nbsp;打印到控制台。</p><pre class=\"prism-token token  language-javascript\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 1em; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background: rgb(80, 85, 107); border-radius: 3px; overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; font-size: 14px;\">package org.zsl.testmybatis;\n\nimport javax.annotation.Resource;\n\nimport org.apache.log4j.Logger;\nimport org.junit.Before;\nimport org.junit.Test;\nimport org.junit.runner.RunWith;\nimport org.springframework.context.ApplicationContext;\nimport org.springframework.context.support.ClassPathXmlApplicationContext;\nimport org.springframework.test.context.ContextConfiguration;