style=\"padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px; background: none rgb(247, 247, 247); border: none; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); min-height: 0px; quotes: none; position: relative; border-radius: 6px; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><p style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; color: rgba(68, 68, 68, 0.9); line-height: 28px; margin-top: -20px !important;\">参考文章：<a href=\"http://blog.didispace.com/springbootswagger2/\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\">http://blog.didispace.com/springbootswagger2/</a></p></blockquote><p style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" lato,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 1.1em;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.015em;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(34,=\"\" 34,=\"\" 34);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.9);\"=\"\">RESTful 风格为后台与前台的交互提供了简洁的接口API，并且有利于减少与其他团队的沟通成本，通常情况下，我们会创建一份RESTful API文档来记录所有的接口细节，但是这样做有以下的几个问题：</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 40px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15.5px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.9);\"=\"\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.5em; list-style: decimal;\">由于接口众多，并且细节复杂（需要考虑不同的HTTP请求类型、HTTP头部信息、HTTP请求内容等），<strong style=\"color: rgb(191, 54, 12);\">高质量地创建这份文档本身就是件非常吃力的事</strong>，下游的抱怨声不绝于耳。</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.5em; list-style: decimal;\">随着时间推移，不断修改接口实现的时候都必须同步修改接口文档，而文档与代码又处于两个不同的媒介，除非有严格的管理机制，不然<strong style=\"color: rgb(191, 54, 12);\">很容易导致不一致现象。</strong></li></ol><p style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" lato,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 1.1em;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.015em;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(34,=\"\" 34,=\"\" 34);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.9);\"=\"\">Swagger2的出现就是为了解决上述的这些问题，并且能够轻松的整合到我们的SpringBoot中去，它既可以减少我们创建文档的工作量，同时说明内容又可以整合到代码之中去，让维护文档和修改代码整合为一体，可以让我们在修改代码逻辑的同时方便的修改文档说明，这太酷了，另外<strong style=\"color: rgb(191, 54, 12);\">Swagger2页提供了强大的页面测试功能来调试每个RESTful API</strong>，具体效果如下：</p><p style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" lato,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 1.1em;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.015em;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(34,=\"\" 34,=\"\" 34);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.9);\"=\"\"><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" href=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7896890-c5e98d9ffb2e2521.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7896890-c5e98d9ffb2e2521.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; height: auto; max-width: 700px; display: block; border-radius: 5px;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" lato,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 1.1em;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.015em;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(34,=\"\" 34,=\"\" 34);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.9);\"=\"\">让我们赶紧来看看吧：</p><h4 id=\"第一步：添加swagger2依赖：\" style=\"padding-l