em; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" lato,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 1.1em;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.015em;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(34,=\"\" 34,=\"\" 34);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.9);\"=\"\">完成上述代码添加之后，启动Spring Boot程序，访问：<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%89%8D%E6%96%87%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84RESTful\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\">http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html，就能看到前文展示的RESTful</a>&nbsp;API的页面，我们可以点开具体的API请求，POST类型的/users请求为例，可找到上述代码中我们配置的Notes信息以及参数user的描述信息，如下图所示：</p><p style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" lato,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 1.1em;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0.015em;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(34,=\"\" 34,=\"\" 34);=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.9);\"=\"\"><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" href=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7896890-dc830a1e2bc8f3f8.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7896890-dc830a1e2bc8f3f8.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; height: auto; max-width: 700px; display: block; border-radius: 5px;\"></a></p><h4 id=\"api文档访问与调试\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.9);\"=\"\">API文档访问与调试</h4><p style=\"padding-right: 20px; pa